snippet: No. 8 Wichita State (28-3), the top seed, defeated ninth-seeded Southern Illinois (12-21), 56-45, in the quarterfinals of the Missouri Valley Conference tournament.
abstract: Wichita State men's basketball team defeats Southern Illinois, 56-45, in Missouri Valley Conference tournament.
